<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Moist2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Moist,</orth> vb. to wet: <emph>write till your ink be dry, and</emph> <cit><quote>with your tears m. it again,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 2, 76</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>no more the juice of Egypt's grape shall m. this lip,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.285" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 285</bibl></cit>.
